index-paragraph-1: Dis chuul shuo $1 kwaalifaiya pan $2 a $3 stietmen dem a ieriya pan de relietin pikcha.
index-paragraph-2: Fu stietmen pan [$1 Wikidieta] aitm dem, dey go see pan de aitm $2 (a oda praapatee). Fu stietmen pan [$3 Strakcha Dieta pan Kaman dem] pikcha dem, dey go see pan de pikcha umself.
index-label-property-id-optional: Praapatee ID <small>(yu no hafu do dis)</small>
image-depicted-without-region: Min shuo wid no reejan min chuuz:
image-named-places-on-map-without-region: Niem plies dem pan maap wid no reejan min chuuz:
alert-not-logged-in: Yu no laag een<noscript> an JaavaSkrip put arf</noscript>, so yu kyaan ongle see existin reejan dem an stietmen dem. Fu put arf nyuu stietmen dem a reejan dem a chienj existin wan dem, [$1 laag een]<noscript> an put arf JaavaSkrip</noscript>.
alert-noscript: JaavaSkrip aaf, so yu kyaan onglee see existin reejan dem an stietmen dem. Fu put arf nyuu reejan dem a stietmen dem a chienj existin wan dem, put arf JaavaSkrip.
file-not-found-body: Wan fail kaal <q>$1</q> no fain. Um kud be misin, a de niem kud be rang.
wrong-data-value-type-paragraph-1: Rang valyuu taip fu de pikcha praapatee: expek $1 but min $2.
wrong-data-value-type-paragraph-2: Did yu put de rang praapatee?
